---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | ChinaSupport" description="About ChinaSupport">
  <div class="stack gap-20">
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 py-16 sm:py-20">
        <h3>China-Support: Your Gateway to Chinese Markets</h3>
        <h4>Our Story</h4>
        <div>
          China-Support was established with a clear vision: to bridge the gap between global businesses and the vast opportunities within the Chinese
          market. Our team, based in the heart of China, has been navigating the complexities of Chinese trade for over a decade, providing
          unparalleled access to high-quality goods and services.
        </div>
        <h4>Our Team</h4>
        <div>
          At China-Support, we pride ourselves on our diverse and dedicated team of professionals with a wealth of experience in international trade,
          sourcing, and customer service. Our expertise lies in understanding both the Western and Chinese business landscapes, ensuring seamless
          communication and efficient solutions for our clients.
        </div>
        <h4>Our Services</h4>
        <div>
          We offer a comprehensive suite of services tailored to meet the unique needs of our clients:
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Product Sourcing:</strong> Finding the right products at the best prices.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Customization:</strong> Personalizing products to fit your brand's identity.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Procurement:</strong> Streamlining the purchasing process.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Market Research:</strong> Delivering insights into market trends and consumer behavior.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Company Auditing:</strong> Providing neutral and detailed reports on Chinese companies.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <h4>Our Philosophy</h4>
        <div>
          Our philosophy is rooted in integrity, professionalism, and a commitment to excellence. We believe in building lasting relationships with
          our clients, based on trust and mutual success. Our goal is not just to meet expectations but to exceed them.
        </div>
        <h4>Our Achievements</h4>
        <div>
          Since our inception, China-Support has helped hundreds of businesses successfully enter and thrive in the Chinese market. We've achieved
          this through a combination of deep market knowledge, personalized service, and a relentless pursuit of quality.
        </div>
        <h4>Our Partners</h4>
        <div>
          We collaborate with a network of reputable partners across various industries, ensuring that our clients have access to the best resources
          and opportunities. Our partnerships are built on shared values of quality, reliability, and innovation.
        </div>
        <h4>Get in Touch</h4>
        <div>
          Ready to unlock the potential of the Chinese market? We are just an email or phone call away. Let's discuss how China-Support can help you
          achieve your business goals.
        </div>
        <h4>Contact Information</h4>
        <div>
          <ul>
            <li>Email: contact@china-support.com</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h4 {
    @apply mt-8 text-xl font-semibold pb-1;
  }
  li {
    @apply ml-4;
    list-style-type: circle;
  }
</style>
